<br>
nah. <br>
<br>
Scene: seb disco, get a pull, and the room pops the second that the cleric lands their first heavy heal, so the pops aggro him. MT goes down, cleric goes down, ranger goes down. left with me, the monk, and a mage.... and four frogs. Lock everything down, CoH the cleric from the zone in, have him rez everyone else and them himself, get everyone rebuffed and ready to go... all while these four frogs are croaking at us.<br>
<br>
